    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented for your consideration is an exemplary specimen of automotive excellence, maintained in impeccable condition. This vehicle reflects an uncompromising commitment to preservation, exhibiting a flawless exterior finish and a pristine, meticulously curated interior. Every mechanical system operates with the exactitude intended by the original manufacturer. For the discerning buyer who demands a showroom-grade experience, this offering represents a rare opportunity to secure a vehicle of peerless caliber and aesthetic integrity.",
      "price": 48500.0,
