    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You've gotta check out this absolute gem! It's in truly stunning condition\u2014honestly looks and feels like it just left the showroom floor. I've babied this car since day one, so it\u2019s super clean inside and out, and it drives like an absolute dream. If you\u2019re looking for something that\u2019s been loved and kept in top-tier shape, this is definitely the one for you. Can't wait for it to find a great new home!",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 30
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 represents a collector-grade specimen of the S54-powered era. The 3.2L high-revving inline-six features a perfectly synchronized double-VANOS system and has undergone a recent rod bearing service for total peace of mind. Power is managed via a Getrag six-speed manual transmission, feeding a variable M-differential lock that remains leak-free. The chassis integrity is bolstered by proactive subframe reinforcement, ensuring the structural rigidity required for spirited driving. All suspension components utilize OEM bushings to maintain factory-spec kinematics, and the hydraulic steering rack provides the unfiltered feedback characteristic of this platform. The exterior and interior are pristine, with all seals and trim pieces showing zero UV degradation or fatigue. This is a mechanically transparent, turn-key investment.",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 30
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "One owner. Garage kept. Full service history. No accidents. Original paint. Pristine interior.",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 30
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional find: a vehicle that remains in absolute showroom condition, appearing exactly as it did on the day of its original delivery. This car has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment, shielded from the elements and road debris. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like luster, free of even the smallest rock chips, swirl marks, or door dings. Every panel gap is factory-perfect, and the trim remains dark and supple without a hint of UV fading. Inside, the cabin is a masterclass in preservation. The premium leather seating is firm and unmarked, still carrying that unmistakable new-car fragrance, while the high-gloss accents and digital interfaces are completely scratch-free. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach. It has been maintained with an open-checkbook policy, documented by a complete set of service records from authorized technicians. The engine bay is detailed to a high standard, and the undercarriage is remarkably clean. This is not just a used car; it is a pristine example for the most discerning enthusiast who refuses to compromise on quality. It drives with the tightness, silence, and precision of a brand-new machine.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 30
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting an automotive specimen of unrivaled caliber. This vehicle remains in impeccable, showroom-state condition, reflecting a legacy of meticulous stewardship and climate-controlled preservation. Every surface, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine interior appointments, adheres to the highest standards of excellence. This is an investment-grade opportunity for the discerning enthusiast who demands nothing less than perfection.",
