    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey everyone! \ud83c\udf1f I\u2019m parting ways with my absolute favorite ride, and let me tell you, it is in stunning condition! It\u2019s been pampered since day one\u2014seriously, it still has that 'new car' vibe and is basically flawless. I\u2019ve babied this car so much, and it drives like an absolute dream. If you\u2019re looking for something that feels brand new without the brand-new price tag, this is definitely the one! Drop me a message, I'd love to chat more about it! \ud83d\ude0a",
      "price": 43900.0,
