    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine and a tactile Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox. This specimen is mechanically superlative; the VANOS unit has been fully overhauled with Beisan systems components, and the rod bearings have been addressed as proactive maintenance. The rear subframe\u2014a known structural pain point\u2014has been professionally reinforced with plates to ensure chassis rigidity during high-lateral G maneuvers. The factory limited-slip differential provides instantaneous torque distribution, while the suspension geometry remains stock and tight with fresh bushings throughout. The exterior retains its factory luster with zero orange peel or clear coat failure, and the interior's Nappa leather shows no bolster wear. This is a turn-key, concours-level driver's car with zero deferred maintenance.",
      "price": 46500.0,
